esearch skills needed to study and improve educational practice the cte area chair is professor claude goldenberg job placement the great majority of doctoral graduates in this area become university professors often in schools or departments of education that have teacher preparation programs others teach in departments that reflect their discipline within cte such as mathematics or english some take program officer or executive roles in non profit research firms or at universities academics apply now master's programs doctoral programs ships daps cte lstd other undergraduate programs courses stanford academic calendar master's handbook doctoral handbook stanford university school of education 485 lasuen mall stanford ca 94305 3096 tel 650 723 2109 copyright 2012 stanford university all rights reserved terms of use copyright complaints site map contact us helpsu suse it axess academic calendar stanford bulletin office of the registrar edmail stanfordwho stanfordyou login connect with us on facebook connect with us on twitter connect with us on youtube connect with us on flickr make a gift now
